features: YO JOE! G.I. JOE EXPLODES INTO A LARGER-THAN-LIFE ERA WITH 6-INCH-SCALE FIGURES: The G.I. Joe Classified Series evolves the characters fans know and love into a highly articulated 6-inch scale with premium deco and detailing

CLASSIC LONZO "STALKER" WILKINSON-INSPIRED DESIGN: This figure features a classic design updated to bring the G.I. Joe Medic and Interpreter into the modern era, plus accessories inspired by the character’s rich history

COLLECTIBLE PACKAGING WITH CUSTOM ART: Joining some of the best artists from the world of comics and graphic design in our artist partnership program, Frank Morrison adds a unique style to the Lonzo "Stalker" Wilkinson package

HIGHLY POSEABLE WITH PREMIUM DETAILING: This G.I. Joe Classified Series Lonzo "Stalker" Wilkinson figure features premium detailing and articulation for dramatic action poseability (some poses may require additional support)
EXPAND YOUR ROSTER: Look for other 6-inch-scale G.I. Joe Classified Series figures and build your roster of heroes and villains (Each sold separately. Subject to availability.)
body.description: G.I. Joe is a highly skilled, on-demand, special operations force of men and women from around the globe. These extraordinarily talented heroes are selected for their elite abilities and tasked with defending the world from Cobra, a ruthless criminal organization bent on total domination. With unwavering courage and steely determination, the brave members of G.I. Joe are prepared to seek out Cobra in any environment on the planet. From hostile jungles to ice-clad arctic peaks…wherever there’s trouble, G.I. Joe is there. This Lonzo "Stalker" Wilkinson figure comes ready for action, with multiple points of articulation for high poseability and 10 character-inspired accessories. And with custom artwork by Frank Morrison, the G.I. Joe Classified Series Lonzo "Stalker" Wilkinson package will make a mark on shelves.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Yo Joe! The world of G.I. Joe has always evolved to reflect the times we live in, and the evolution continues with the Classified Series. Whether you’re dipping your toe into collecting G.I. Joe figures for the first time, the fifth time, or the four hundredth time, the G.I. Joe Classified Series line of action figures captures the pulse-pounding excitement of G.I. Joe in a 6-inch scale. And it’s all showcased in collectible display-worthy packaging featuring custom artwork by talented artists from around the world, commissioned by Hasbro to put their iconic stamps on classic characters.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Hands down one of the best releases in the Joe Classified line
reviews.reviewText: Easily one of the best sets in the whole Joe Classified lineup so far. Has a ton of gear, all of which can be worn on the figure. And he looks great geared up with none of the weird proportion issues that plagued figures like Lt.Falcon and Roadblock. Comes with pieces to do both his classic look and something a little more modern (but not too modern). Overall, a must get.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great Figure, Can't Say As Much About the Box
reviews.reviewText: The goal of G.I. Joe is to defend the world from Cobra, a ruthless criminal organization bent on total supremacy. The team is made up of men and women from all over the world who specialize in special operations and are picked for their remarkable skills. G.I. Joe is there wherever danger exists, from icy polar tops to vicious jungles.This six-inch Lonzo "Stalker Wilkinson figurine is prepared for battle, including ten accessories inspired by the characters, and many points of articulation for maximum poseability. Along with the figure, ten accessories are included. Due to how detailed it is, collectors will want to own it.These are not actually toys, despite what they were first intended to be. They are a little expensive for that, and the package specifically warns against using them with children under the age of four since they could choke them. Finding the right ones might be difficult, but I was fortunate to discover this one online. Although the figure itself is wonderful, the packaging regrettably wasn't in as good of shape, which reduces the value of my figure and collection.
